item.title: CVE-2023-33955|2024-08-02T15:54:14.094Z -- minio -- console
item.description: Minio Console is the UI for MinIO Object Storage. Unicode RIGHT-TO-LEFT OVERRIDE characters can be used to mask the original filename. This issue has been patched in version 0.28.0.
